<article id="post-170" class="post-170 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-home tag-j-k-galbraith">
    <div class="entry-content background_color_6">
        	<div>
		<span class='first_letter_big'>F</span>aced with the choice between changing one&#8217;s mind and proving that there is no need to do so, almost everyone gets busy on the proof.

		<div style="display:inline; white-space: nowrap; padding-top:10px; color:#333">
			<span class='the_tilde'>~</span>
	 		<span class='the_author'><!-- 00  00 --><a href="http://www.canadianquotations.ca/tag/j-k-galbraith" rel="tag">J. K. Galbraith - Canadian/American economist</a><!-- 11 --> </span>
